(3452, 229, 'list_3_content', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The painting depicts three majestic sunflowers, each standing tall and proud. The vibrant yellow petals of the sunflowers are distinctly visible, emphasizing their exuberance and warmth. The painting captures the intricate details of the flowers’ large, round centers, which contain numerous seeds intricately layered within them. The background is filled with a deep greenery, drawing attention to the flowers\' details. The brushstrokes used in the painting give it a sense of movement and texture, providing a sense of depth and life to the painting. Overall it is an enchanting display of nature at its glorious best.</span>'),
